Place angel food cake cubes in bottom of an oval casserole or trifle dish. Combine 1/2 cup coffee creamer and Equal(r). Drizzle creamer mixture over cake. Top cake with mango, pineapple and bananas. Beat cream cheese until smooth. Gradually beat in remaining 1 cup coffee creamer. Gently fold in whipped topping. Spread cream cheese mixture over fruit. Sprinkle with toasted coconut, if desired. Refrigerate 2 to 3 hours before serving.